[size=4][b][u]Overview[/u][/b][/size]
Cora Coe has come through Unity to continue her hunt for good books to populate her library with. She also needs help hunting down the people who killed her universe's Constellation group and more importantly her Father.

This mod will expand over the next 2-3 months to a DLC sized mod with a full main quest line, branching side quests, new game systems, a new faction with a new outer rim home planet. My plan is to get this done with xEdit just to push the edge of what we can do without official tools. That being said, as soon as I get my hands on a copy of CK2 this will be converted over too it for safety.

[quote]NOTE: This is very much a beta. She is implemented in minimum companion mode right now using only the Support/Sniper template.[/quote]

[size=4][b][u]Features[/u][/b][/size]
[list]
[*]Full companion with text lines (Voice Lines Coming)
[*]Like kid Cora she takes all the books again. Going forward fixes on either side will be added to both.
[*]Currently only the sniper support mage skill package is implemented
[*]She uses Starborn death mechanic which means when killed she vanishes and teleports near by this is by design not a bug :) 
[/list]

