[size=4][b][u]Usage[/u][/b][/size]
She will approach you in the Lodge on completion of Unearthed or having entered Unity at least once. Her spawn point is near the mark 1 suit in the basement. (Beta note this is disabled currently need feedback)

[b][u]Installation [/u][/b]
[size=3][b]Via Vortex/MO2[/b][/size]
Install as normally would any mod mod. 

[size=3][b]Installation Manually[/b][/size]
Really please use a mod manage :) 

Download the current zip file. Please everything in the Data folder in the zip to the same place under <Game Install Dir aka where starfield.exe is>\Data.

[size=3][b]Handling the plugins.txt file[/b][/size]
You need to add CoraCoeMultiversalBookHunter.esm, BooksRevamped.esm, CoraCanRead.esm, and VenpiCore.esm to your plugins.txt file see below for help. Should be ordered like this in the file.

[code]
*VenpiCore.esm
*BooksRevamped.esm
*CoraCanRead.esm
*CoraCoeMultiversalBookHunter.esm
[/code]

If you are using one of the alternative looks for cora you need the following load order. Replace CoraCoeMultiversalBookHunter-AltLook1.esm which ever alternative look you choose. 

[code]
*VenpiCore.esm
*BooksRevamped.esm
*CoraCanRead.esm
*CoraCoeMultiversalBookHunter.esm
*CoraCoeMultiversalBookHunter-AltLook1.esm
[/code]


